window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Errant wives with <b>bratty</b> mouthes and lots of <em>attitude</em> find themselves turned <b>over the knee</b> of their <b>dominant</b> husbands as they teach them their place.</p><p>Jenny can't stop spending money on Christmas presents she doesn't need, so Matt grabs a <em>hairbrush</em> and shows her what overdrafting his patience will do to her backside. Mark isn't enjoying his honeymoon with his grouchy new bride, so he takes her <b>over his knee</b> on the side of the road to help her cheer up. Abigail can't keep her sass to herself, so Dalton gives her the <b>attitude adjustment</b> that she's clearly asking for until she's crying and begging him to stop.</p><p>Join these ladies as they are taught to respect their husbands the old fashioned way.</p><ul><li>Overdrafting: Spanked Wives Series</li><li>Roadside Discipline: Spanked Wives Series</li><li>Attitude Adjustment: Spanked Wives Series<br></li></ul><br><p><u><b>Spanked Wives Series Bundle</b></u> features over 9,000 words of <b>domestic discipline</b> among <em>consenting adults</em>. Attitudes are adjusted, <b>punishments</b> are meted out, and wives are set straight. Join these ladies as their <b>bottoms</b> get roasted and their marriages are saved. This is a work of <em>fiction</em> and is meant to be treated as such.</p><p>★ Enjoy! ★<br></p>"; 
